      Indulge in artful cuisine, unwind in style at our captivating lounge bar. Flavors ignite, music sets.
    </p>
    <!-- Dual Actions -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="/menu" class="gsap-hero-btn btn-hover bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover text-background-dark font-semibold h-11 sm:h-12 px-6 sm:px-8 rounded-full transition-colors text-sm sm:text-base shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 flex items-center">
        Explore Menu
